Eat up.

887
00:38:04,480 --> 00:38:04,880
Go on.

888
00:38:04,980 --> 00:38:06,150
Why don't I understand?

889
00:38:06,580 --> 00:38:08,230
It's just that our families have a grudge.

890
00:38:08,410 --> 00:38:09,900
They think their family is much more well-off

891
00:38:09,920 --> 00:38:10,520
than ours.

892
00:38:11,310 --> 00:38:12,380
It's really annoying.

893
00:38:13,920 --> 00:38:15,200
Not only that.

894
00:38:15,830 --> 00:38:16,920
I think

895
00:38:16,950 --> 00:38:17,950
you are just stubborn.

896
00:38:18,350 --> 00:38:19,870
What do people pursue in this day and age?

897
00:38:20,790 --> 00:38:21,740
It's

898
00:38:21,760 --> 00:38:22,840
freedom and happiness,

899
00:38:22,880 --> 00:38:23,720
and being in the moment.

900
00:38:24,030 --> 00:38:25,310
If you like each other, then be together.

901
00:38:25,760 --> 00:38:26,890
The future is so far away.

902
00:38:26,920 --> 00:38:28,310
Forget about getting married.

903
00:38:28,350 --> 00:38:29,450
Just date first.

904
00:38:29,790 --> 00:38:30,840
Wherever you end up is fine.

905
00:38:30,880 --> 00:38:31,800
Date if you can.

906
00:38:31,820 --> 00:38:32,790
Break up if it doesn't work.

907
00:38:33,050 --> 00:38:34,700
It's better than how you are now.

908
00:38:34,840 --> 00:38:35,970
Thinking about the distant future

909
00:38:36,010 --> 00:38:37,130
and so far away from each other.

910
00:38:38,030 --> 00:38:38,780
At least you will have enjoyed

911
00:38:38,810 --> 00:38:39,900
your time together.

912
00:38:40,250 --> 00:38:41,180
Besides,

913
00:38:41,250 --> 00:38:42,490
if you two date again,

914
00:38:42,740 --> 00:38:43,730
if you find out

915
00:38:43,750 --> 00:38:44,550
her true colors,

916
00:38:44,650 --> 00:38:45,730
you might not like her anymore.

917
00:38:45,750 --> 00:38:46,550
Then, you can let her go.

918
00:38:46,580 --> 00:38:47,220
That's great.

919
00:38:47,630 --> 00:38:49,070
Why do you have so many heretic ideas?

920
00:38:49,100 --> 00:38:50,500
They're not heretic.

921
00:38:50,570 --> 00:38:51,450
Who says that dating

922
00:38:51,490 --> 00:38:52,680
has to end well?

923
00:38:52,800 --> 00:38:53,400
Brother.

924
00:38:53,590 --> 00:38:54,700
You have a face

925
00:38:54,720 --> 00:38:56,480
that can get you into multiple romances,

926
00:38:56,510 --> 00:38:57,500
but you have a heart

927
00:38:57,530 --> 00:38:58,620
that only wants forever with one person.

928
00:39:01,220 --> 00:39:02,610
You can stop talking now.

929
00:39:02,920 --> 00:39:03,880
Eat up.

930
00:39:04,950 --> 00:39:06,040
Okay, thank you.

931
00:39:06,240 --> 00:39:07,040
Enjoy.

932
00:39:09,460 --> 00:39:10,390
Are you serious?

933
00:39:11,230 --> 00:39:11,940
What?

934
00:39:12,030 --> 00:39:12,790
Stop pretending.

935
00:39:13,070 --> 00:39:13,960
I'm talking about Song Yan.

936
00:39:17,700 --> 00:39:18,860
I admire you.

937
00:39:19,870 --> 00:39:21,490
Can you let it go?

938
00:39:21,920 --> 00:39:22,810
There are plenty of opportunities

939
00:39:22,840 --> 00:39:24,110
to be happy in life.

940
00:39:24,480 --> 00:39:25,270
What are you doing?

941
00:39:26,080 --> 00:39:27,260
I really wish

942
00:39:27,290 --> 00:39:28,010
I were like you.

943
00:39:30,740 --> 00:39:31,850
Tell me then.

944
00:39:32,070 --> 00:39:33,050
What exactly

945
00:39:33,090 --> 00:39:34,040
about Song Yan

946
00:39:34,070 --> 00:39:34,990
is worth you liking him?

947
00:39:36,610 --> 00:39:37,440
I don't know.

948
00:39:38,750 --> 00:39:40,010
That means you like him very much.

949
00:39:40,810 --> 00:39:41,860
Are you against it too?

950
00:39:43,030 --> 00:39:44,150
That's not very kind

951
00:39:44,500 --> 00:39:45,650
of you to say.

952
00:39:46,140 --> 00:39:47,330
When have I opposed it

953
00:39:47,350 --> 00:39:48,720
when you two used to date?

954
00:39:51,060 --> 00:39:51,910
But now,

955
00:39:52,090 --> 00:39:53,930
I have to analyze it for you.

956
00:39:55,270 --> 00:39:56,110
Let me ask you.

957
00:39:56,640 --> 00:39:58,290
If your mother is firmly opposed to it no matter what,

958
00:39:58,550 --> 00:39:59,840
if she thinks his parents are no good,

959
00:39:59,870 --> 00:40:00,540
his family is poor,

960
00:40:00,630 --> 00:40:02,400
and insists that you find someone from a suitable family,

961
00:40:02,970 --> 00:40:03,710
what will you do?

962
00:40:05,300 --> 00:40:07,150
Some things are usually invisible.

963
00:40:07,310 --> 00:40:08,580
Once you talk about marriage,

964
00:40:08,710 --> 00:40:10,070
they will become problems.

965
00:40:10,790 --> 00:40:11,830
Don't blame your mother.

966
00:40:12,240 --> 00:40:13,670
She sees more clearly than you do.

967
00:40:14,460 --> 00:40:15,990
Love is fleeting.

968
00:40:16,430 --> 00:40:17,400
Reality is the mountain

969
00:40:17,420 --> 00:40:18,790
no one can move.

970
00:40:23,070 --> 00:40:24,880
But only when I see him

971
00:40:27,650 --> 00:40:29,610
do I feel alive.

972
00:40:33,300 --> 00:40:34,580
You're going to be the death of me.

973
00:40:36,760 --> 00:40:37,820
Speaking of which,

974
00:40:38,660 --> 00:40:40,050
is Song Yan on the same page?

975
00:40:40,070 --> 00:40:41,390
Does he think so too?

976
00:40:42,640 --> 00:40:43,880
You saw what Song Yan was like

977
00:40:45,390 --> 00:40:46,990
at the police station.

978
00:40:47,850 --> 00:40:49,530
Your mother and brother don't like him.

979
00:40:49,750 --> 00:40:51,490
He's known it all along.

980
00:40:51,770 --> 00:40:53,460
Today, your brother humiliated him to his face.

981
00:40:54,570 --> 00:40:56,220
He's so proud.

982
00:40:56,600 --> 00:40:58,480
How can he not resent you?

983
00:40:59,080 --> 00:41:00,300
If he can let go of his pride

984
00:41:00,320 --> 00:41:01,500
and be with you,

985
00:41:01,520 --> 00:41:03,370
I'll think he's more unreliable.

986
00:41:05,560 --> 00:41:06,880
Listen to me.

987
00:41:07,670 --> 00:41:08,870
You two are not suitable for each other.

988
00:41:10,040 --> 00:41:10,830
Really.
